{"tid":27462,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"返工工時長，做下自己野有冇問題？","createTime":"2016-12-07T10:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T15:53:57.000Z","uid":19386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"53a5f1fbf118dd726e73ea3459d9f9f58171e438","tid":27462,"uid":19386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:37:43.000Z","msg":"一日返成9個幾10個鐘，老細好似expect要每一秒都好精神做野咁，我一睇下手機，閉目養神一下，或者上下網睇一兩分鍾新聞，都已經開聲話我<br />\n<br />\n返工工時咁長，係咪用15分鐘做下自己野都唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3173b58436f998fee80c5eb05e4adca10a1733c","tid":27462,"uid":39695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:38:50.000Z","msg":"出黎打工預左係咁，有路數轉咪走人"},{"pid":"7c4f729d9d72205e996bd20e9fc5e87d6854901f","tid":27462,"uid":45914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:40:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f36990d854b9ee8682f76f63e4ae3691ddd3d37b","tid":27462,"uid":19386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出黎打工預左係咁，有路數轉咪走人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能我以前返工𠴱度好人性化，幾年嚟生活左係溫室度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3c1a30d654363a7e753ae7e24f60856a7d1479","tid":27462,"uid":52936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:41:05.000Z","msg":"返工做自己野多過做公司野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9bc02e6284a1e93d4704dda4361d30f7a0296a","tid":27462,"uid":19386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:41:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返工做自己野多過做公司野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊行呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2927648f1ba3ef23f7459a6868a97d57f7d72742","tid":27462,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:43:27.000Z","msg":"返工唔做自己野？傻架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad17ec1c36ae2a656ebf4ef4453362b078706f04","tid":27462,"uid":19386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:47:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返工唔做自己野？傻架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌佢老母我做左成朝野，然後下晝4點幾見攰攰地，俾自己休息一下，睇下新聞咁，然後就叫左我埋去同我講：「大家都係成年人，你知你依家咩情況，返工時候唔好做自己野啦」<br />\n<br />\n我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258ca9440770d333cb7e2bfaceca6659e4709fa5","tid":27462,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:51:09.000Z","msg":"屌咩<br />\n返工唔通真係每日做9個鐘野呀<br />\n起碼要有3分1時間做自己野上下網之類<br />\n又唔係簽賣身契<br />\n最緊要係準時交到貨"},{"pid":"cfb169482793f411c7b9085e10472a65373e610d","tid":27462,"uid":52936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:10:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>返工做自己野多過做公司野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊行呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n製作釘裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523722653022f1d79d4b2050ccf447852f155d79","tid":27462,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:28:08.000Z","msg":"而家啲90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d57cdf33aaf695a27b1c5449ffd81820b0d23de4","tid":27462,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:44:30.000Z","msg":"西公司<br />\n你喺度都唔會有咩發展"},{"pid":"251efc6fad93495f317dc57727f6e331e4cf26ae","tid":27462,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:53:57.000Z","msg":"有d公司只要你準時交到貨, 話之你遲到早退做自己野<br />\n<br />\n有d你要你每秒都做緊野先得"}]}